Restock essentials: fresh towels, toilet paper, hand soap, shampoo, etc. Kitchen Wipe down all surfaces, including countertops, stovetop, and oven. Dishes. Dishes should be done by the guest, but some guest forget. Clean sink and run garbage disposal with soap and water. Sweep/mop the floor, removing crumbs and spills. Restock: paper towels, dish soap, clean sponge, etc. (Extras of all this will be at the unit. You should have some extra tp and trashbags just in case. I will refund you) General Areas Dust all surfaces (tables, electronics, shelves). Vacuum/sweep/mop floors—including under furniture and corners. Check and change linens: fresh sheets and pillowcases on all beds. Take out all trash and replace liners. Look carefully for hair (especially in bathrooms and on linens). Report any damages, missing items, or maintenance issues. Usually the spaces are pretty clean because they are cleaned so often.  Outdoor Areas Sweep and Tidy

Address: 1903 Cottle Avenue, Sanger, CA, USA
Provider note: ✅General Guidelines Wear gloves & use fresh cloths/mop heads per room Check for guest items left behind Take before/after photos if required Turn off all lights and A/C before leaving Report damage, missing items, or low supplies 🛏️ Bedrooms Strip beds completely(sheets, pillowcases, comforters) Replace with fresh, clean linens and fluff pillows Dust all surfaces, including headboards and nightstands Wipe mirrors, clean windows Vacuum floors and under the bed Empty trash & replace liner 🛁 Bathrooms Scrub and disinfect toilet, sink, and tub/shower Clean mirrors and polish faucets Replace used towels with clean ones (bath, hand, washcloth) Restock: toilet paper (2+ rolls), soap, shampoo, conditioner Empty trash, replace liner Mop floor, check for hair and residue 🍽️ Kitchen Wipe countertops, sink, stove, and backsplash Clean inside microwave & fridge shelves Run or unload dishwasher (clean all dishes) Restock: paper towels, dish soap, sponge, trash bags Empty trash and replace liner Sweep and mop floors 🛋️ Living Room / Common Areas Dust all surfaces (tables, shelves, remotes) Fluff pillows and fold blankets Wipe down mirrors, windows, and glass surfaces Vacuum floor and area rugs Ensure remotes, Wi-Fi info, and welcome guide are in place Empty trash & replace liner 🧺 Laundry (Linens & Towels) Start laundry first if in-unit washer/dryer is available Wash towels and bedding on appropriate settings (hot/warm) Dry fully and neatly fold or place in designated closets Double-check for stains before reusing If laundry is off-site, collect items in labeled bags 🚪 Entryway Sweep or vacuum entrance Clean door glass and handles Neatly place welcome mat Ensure check-in instructions or binder is present 🧼 Final Walkthrough Check for odors, stains, or leftover mess Make sure lights, A/C, and appliances are off Secure the property and lock doors Send completion message or photos if required

Address: 1903 Cottle Avenue, Sanger, CA, USA
Provider note: ✅General Guidelines Wear gloves & use fresh cloths/mop heads per room Check for guest items left behind Take before/after photos if required Turn off all lights and A/C before leaving Report damage, missing items, or low supplies 🛏️ Bedrooms Strip beds completely(sheets, pillowcases, comforters) Replace with fresh, clean linens and fluff pillows Dust all surfaces, including headboards and nightstands Wipe mirrors, clean windows Vacuum floors and under the bed Empty trash & replace liner 🛁 Bathrooms Scrub and disinfect toilet, sink, and tub/shower Clean mirrors and polish faucets Replace used towels with clean ones (bath, hand, washcloth) Restock: toilet paper (2+ rolls), soap, shampoo, conditioner Empty trash, replace liner Mop floor, check for hair and residue 🍽️ Kitchen Wipe countertops, sink, stove, and backsplash Clean inside microwave & fridge shelves Run or unload dishwasher (clean all dishes) Restock: paper towels, dish soap, sponge, trash bags Empty trash and replace liner Sweep and mop floors 🛋️ Living Room / Common Areas Dust all surfaces (tables, shelves, remotes) Fluff pillows and fold blankets Wipe down mirrors, windows, and glass surfaces Vacuum floor and area rugs Ensure remotes, Wi-Fi info, and welcome guide are in place Empty trash & replace liner 🧺 Laundry (Linens & Towels) Start laundry first if in-unit washer/dryer is available Wash towels and bedding on appropriate settings (hot/warm) Dry fully and neatly fold or place in designated closets Double-check for stains before reusing If laundry is off-site, collect items in labeled bags 🚪 Entryway Sweep or vacuum entrance Clean door glass and handles Neatly place welcome mat Ensure check-in instructions or binder is present 🧼 Final Walkthrough Check for odors, stains, or leftover mess Make sure lights, A/C, and appliances are off Secure the property and lock doors Send completion message or photos if required

Provider note: ✅General Guidelines Wear gloves & use fresh cloths/mop heads per room Check for guest items left behind Take before/after photos if required Turn off all lights and A/C before leaving Report damage, missing items, or low supplies 🛏️ Bedrooms Strip beds completely(sheets, pillowcases, comforters) Replace with fresh, clean linens and fluff pillows Dust all surfaces, including headboards and nightstands Wipe mirrors, clean windows Vacuum floors and under the bed Empty trash & replace liner 🛁 Bathrooms Scrub and disinfect toilet, sink, and tub/shower Clean mirrors and polish faucets Replace used towels with clean ones (bath, hand, washcloth) Restock: toilet paper (2+ rolls), soap, shampoo, conditioner Empty trash, replace liner Mop floor, check for hair and residue 🍽️ Kitchen Wipe countertops, sink, stove, and backsplash Clean inside microwave & fridge shelves Run or unload dishwasher (clean all dishes) Restock: paper towels, dish soap, sponge, trash bags Empty trash and replace liner Sweep and mop floors 🛋️ Living Room / Common Areas Dust all surfaces (tables, shelves, remotes) Fluff pillows and fold blankets Wipe down mirrors, windows, and glass surfaces Vacuum floor and area rugs Ensure remotes, Wi-Fi info, and welcome guide are in place Empty trash & replace liner 🧺 Laundry (Linens & Towels) Start laundry first if in-unit washer/dryer is available Wash towels and bedding on appropriate settings (hot/warm) Dry fully and neatly fold or place in designated closets Double-check for stains before reusing If laundry is off-site, collect items in labeled bags 🚪 Entryway Sweep or vacuum entrance Clean door glass and handles Neatly place welcome mat Ensure check-in instructions or binder is present 🧼 Final Walkthrough Check for odors, stains, or leftover mess Make sure lights, A/C, and appliances are off Secure the property and lock doors Send completion message or photos if required
